
1  “Entoning ele rorei, ntae nkishu e Bashan, naatii oldoinyo le Samaria, nena naaibooki olaisinani enkop neitorogony olomena nena naajoki ilpayiani lenye, ‘Eyau pee kitum atook!’ 
2  Einosa Olaitoriani olmumai te sinyatisho enye, nchere, ng'ura kepuonu nkolong'i shumata intae, peyie eyau intae too lala oo loolo o metabaiki iloobayie linyi too lala oo loolo loo sinkir. 
3  Naa ipuopuo intae aaim esuntai nataaraki neitashe pooki ng'ae te dukuya ninye nepuoi aanang'aki intae Harmon,” Olaitoriani ojo.

Eitu eiteng'enuo Israel


4  “Wou Betel, tigila nkitanapat, Wou Gilgal, toponai engilata oo nkitanapat; iyau ilasarri linono anaake tadekenya, o matuan inono e tomon te pooki olong e uni. 
5  Intayu olasar le nashe; eina naisuijieki nimbalie inkishorunot e mpiris nilikioo ninche amu inyorrinyorro aaikuna neijia, lo tung'ana le Israel!” Olaitoriani ojo.


6  “Nanu oyaua olameyu atua nkanas inyi pooki o enkiishunoto oo mukateni too nkajijik inyi pooki, ore ake eyia neitu intae kishukokinono nanu,” Olaitoriani ojo.


7  “Naa nanu sii oibooyie enchan meshaiki intae eton eng'or ilapaitin okuni le nkisampuare nairriwaki; nanu enchan shumata e nkanasa nabo napal enkae anasa atashaikia ewueji nebo ore ewueji neitu eshaiki netoyu; 
8  neaku ore iloo nkanas are aashu uni nepuo enkanasa nabo pee eok enkare, nemeishunye ninche enkure; ore eyia neitu intae kirinyokinono nanu,” Olaitoriani ojo.


9  “Ataara indaiki inyi te nkeeya naitomijoon inkurman inyi aitoi isabibu linyi; ore ilng'abolo o loirienito linyi neinos olmaati; ore eyia neitu kishukokinono nanu,” Olaitoriani ojo.


10  “Airriwaka nanu atua intae olmeitai anaa apa enaikununo te Misiri; naar nanu ilbarnot linyi to lalem; naya nanu imbartan inji aiwuang'ie naya nanu olng'usil loo lng'oborri linyi apik nkumeishin inyi; ore eyia eitu intae kishukokinono nanu,” Olaitoriani ojo.


11   “Aidakie nanu ilkulikae te ntae, anaa apa pee eidaikie Enkai Sodom o Gomora, nitiuu apa anaa olmishire oitayioki tiatua enkima nayupuyup; ore eyia eitu intae kishukokinono nanu,” Olaitoriani ojo.


12  “Neaku ena nanu aaitaas, iyie Israel, ore enkaraki naa kaas nanu ena terretenayu pee itumore Enkai ino iyie Israel!”


13  Amu ore ilo oitobira ildoinyo neitayu osiuo, neibalakinye iltung'ana enaikununo endamunoto enye; ilo oitomisimis enkakenya neroro ineeika enkop – Olaitoriani, Enkai oo lororani, ninye enkarna enye!

